Valkyries

I have done a similar model previously but it wasn't "Norse" enough.

Here's an update!

IMPORTANT

Don't expect perfect wings all the time please, they are fickle and I will attempt to fix them in an ulterior update.

DO NOT, underate this model because of wings, I DO NOT advertise perfect wings all the time. If you do underate because of wings you WILL be reported to mod staff, and you WILL NOT have a version of this model with better wings in the future.

You have been warned.
